Understanding Continuations — With Examples in Scheme

These is a PDF version of a blog  article¹, and a couple of slides to illu-
strate the  concept and applications  of full, unbounded  continuations, as
found in some programming languages such as Scheme and Standard ML.

The article is available in PDF form in:

    continuations.pdf

The slides used in a workplace lightning talk are available in:

    continuation-slides.pdf

Both the articles and the slides are covered by Creative Commons BY-SA 4.0².

¹ http://bewatermyfriend.org/p/2019/002/
² https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/
